    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "wait, why would we just gloss over them tho? our clients are going to be in places like Tokyo, Dubai, or Lagos too. i don't want to ignore those regions, i just want to know what the \"standard\" version of professional behavior is so we can have a consistent brand voice. don't you think there's a core set of behaviors that defines being \"sophisticated\" regardless of the country?",
