      "content": "that's a pretty bold take lol. so when you say \"being well-spoken\" or having \"poise,\" are you saying that's basically just following Western social norms? if someone is using a different dialect or has different body language customs that are actually very respectful in their own culture, would you still categorize that as \"unsophisticated\" in a professional guide?",
